Package de.rwth.swc.coffee4j.junit.provider.configuration.reporter

Annotation Type ReporterSource

  • @Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,METHOD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Repeatable(ReporterSources.class)
public @interface ReporterSource
    ReporterSource is an annotation used to register reporter providers for the annotated test method.

    This may also be used as a meta-annotation in order to create a custom composed annotation that inherits the semantics of ReporterSource (demonstrated by Reporter).

    This annotation is repeatable via ReporterSources, and as such multiple providers can be registered.

    This is more or less a copy of ArgumentsSource from the junit-jupiter-params project.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element Description
      java.lang.Class<? extends ReporterProvider> value  

    • Element Detail
